These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-1::.
There 7 different types of food: potato, grapes, cauliflower, kiwi, raspberry, onion, lime
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris, begonia, amaryllis, azalea, sunflower, lily
 1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 2. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 3. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
 4. the person who growslily is the person eating potato##1
 5. the person who growsiris is the person eating kiwi##1
 6. the person who growszinnia is in the middle##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
 9. the person who growssunflower is in an odd position##4
10. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
11. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
12. the person eating cauliflower is the person who growsazalea##1
13. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating onion##1
14. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |    7    |
| Food   | raspberry      | cauliflower      | onion    | lime    | grapes | potato     | kiwi     |
| Flower   | amaryllis | azalea | begonia | zinnia | sunflower   | lily | iris |

