.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: lacrosse, ice-hockey, water-polo, rowing, basketball, sailing, cricket
7 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, canasta, chess, go, domino, snooker
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 2. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 3. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
 4. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person playing domino is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person playing go##1
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is the person playing domino##1
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person playing domino and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
11. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1
12. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |      5      |     6     |   7    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | water-polo | rowing | sailing   | cricket | lacrosse | basketball |
| Game           | go | bridge          | domino    | monopoly | chess     | canasta      | snooker    |

