.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rugby, handball, lacrosse, parkour, climbing, basketball, snowboarding
House: futuristic, victorian, ranch-style, wooden, farmhouse, cottage, modern
 1. the ranch-style house is on the right of the modern house##1
 2. the modern house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
 4. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 5. the cottage house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
 6. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
 8. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
 9. the victorian house is the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
11. the cottage house is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
12. the farmhouse house is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |       5        |        6        |     7      |
| Sport   | parkour        | handball  | basketball | lacrosse | climbing           | snowboarding           | rugby  |
| House    | futuristic | wooden | modern   | ranch-style    | farmhouse | cottage | victorian |

