.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, juice, hot-chocolate, lemonade, fanta, milk
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: marigold, zinnia, lily, aconite, bellflower, dahlia, balloon-flower
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 3. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
 7. the person who growsaconite is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
12. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4      |      5       |      6      |      7      |
| Beverage   | juice | fanta    | hot-chocolate | soy-milk | lemonade      | almond-milk | milk |
| Flower     | balloon-flower  | marigold | aconite   | lily  | dahlia | bellflower     | zinnia    |

