.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-18::.
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, tower, farmhouse, palace, cape-cod, modern
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, zombie, animation, time-travel, mystery, western
 1. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
 2. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
 3. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 4. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
 5. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 7. the tower house is in an even position##4
 8. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 9. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
10. the modern house is between the person watching animation movies and the cape-cod house##2
11. the farmhouse house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
12. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4   |    5    |       6       |      7      |
| House   | palace     | cape-cod   | modern      | tower | gothic-revival    | farmhouse | art-deco |
| Movie-Genre       | zombie | horror | time-travel | animation  | western | documentary     | mystery    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-19::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, skateboard, snowmobile, subway, roller, car, trike
7 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rabbit, frog, fish, turtle, horse, goat
 1. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the horse##1
 2. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 3. the owner of the turtle is the person driving the trike##1
 4. the owner of the goat is the person driving the car##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is in the middle##1
 6. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the roller is the owner of the frog##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
11. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
12. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
13. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
14. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |     5     |    6    |    7    |
| Transport          | subway  | skateboard | motorbike     | trike  | snowmobile | car    | roller  |
| Pet   | fish | horse  | hedgehog | turtle | rabbit | goat | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-20::.
City: new-york, marseilles, miami, san-francisco, edinburgh, nizza, paris
There are 7 different favourite colors: fuchsia, mauve, blood-red, green, black, red, light-blue
 1. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
 2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
 3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 4. the person who likes black is on the far left##1
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who likes mauve##1
 6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 7. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 9. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4
10. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
11. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
12. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |   5    |      6      |    7     |
| City          | nizza   | miami | paris | new-york | edinburgh | marseilles | san-francisco |
| Color   | black | light-blue      | red     | blood-red  | green | fuchsia         | mauve    |

 